# Pupload-LAHACKS — environment template.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in the values you need.
# Anything you set as a real OS env var (`export FOO=bar`) takes
# precedence over the corresponding entry here, so keep them in sync
# or just commit to one source of truth per variable.
#
# Loaded by `cmd/server/main.go` via `github.com/joho/godotenv` on boot.

# --- Server ---------------------------------------------------------
# PORT=8080
# DB_PATH=./pupload-lahacks.db
# CORS_ORIGIN=*
# APP_ENV=production

# --- Pupload controller --------------------------------------------
# Pupload's execution backend. Empty disables Run/Publish (the editor
# still works in read-only mode but those endpoints will return 502).
# PUPLOAD_CONTROLLER_URL=http://localhost:1234

# --- Anthropic / Claude (AI generation) ----------------------------
# Required for the Sparkles button to do real AI generation. Empty
# falls back to a hardcoded sample flow so the demo keeps working.
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Override only if you want a non-default model or proxy / Bedrock.
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-5
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.anthropic.com
